Hi, it's Tim Westergren (ex Pandora Founder & CEO), I'm working on a new product. We're funded by A16Z. I'm looking for an energetic, creative, scrappy full stack engineer who is fully immersed in the latest advances in AI to drive our new product development, experimentation. We want to work with someone who is motivated to ship 0 to 1 and take lead on our engineering efforts, from AI stack to front-end.  We offer competitive comp and equity. You must be a strong communicator with decent English skills.  This is a chance to be a thought-partner and innovator at the ground floor.
